    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the VAD hemolysis CFD model has been reviewed. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed. While several factors show gaps between required and achieved levels (notably model form and discretization error at off-design points), the overall evidence package supports acceptance for the intended regulatory submission context. Monte Carlo UQ has been performed and NIH predictions are within acceptable bounds at the primary design operating point. The assessment team accepts the package with noted limitations.",
